{"tid":1909103,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"湖北大軍番黎播毒+減息救市失敗, 呢個星期恆指會點","createTime":"2020-03-03T17:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T04:25:58.000Z","uid":254330,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"21de46e0483b3a7ad393b9158ef1ae67fd3e48fd","tid":1909103,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:29:35.000Z","msg":"有五百隻湖北蝗蟲黎緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 可能連命都冇, 唔好講炒股了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話要隔離14日可能10日就可以出番條街播毒, 係湖北困左咁耐梗係要出黎唱番次K, 打個邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有每日一萬隻純種支那狗黎播毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 隨時第N波社區爆發, 到時可能真係大規模停工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 真正冇人出街<br />\n<br />\n支那得8萬宗真係冇人信, 實際數字如果網軍控制唔住比醫生爆左出黎, 又係一個大跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再睇下yen同黃金 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過咁, 我代表熊軍多謝支那香港省省長林鄭, 呢排入熊真係有政府, 唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abeda3eeed4c4563ff44493a64e14d54b7c8f1d","tid":1909103,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:30:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.worldometers.info/coronavirus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldometers.info%2Fcoronavirus%2F&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeISL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=728cd739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldometers.info/coronavirus/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國103宗,香港101宗,但係睇黎過埋聽日香港可以超越番美國同新加坡了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd42749e6c4d5eb86331f85f04bb494413c39a20","tid":1909103,"uid":193361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:33:48.000Z","msg":"你估美國少野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"afe51028b1ad230c1a608006afe7b069accef860","tid":1909103,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:34:51.000Z","msg":"rescue flights for more than 500 Hongkongers in outbreak&rsquo;s epicentre<br />\n<br />\nrescue? 邊個被拯救啊"},{"pid":"bfc9016b0d9304c68c054cc1e434f8cca256a685","tid":1909103,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd42749e6c4d5eb86331f85f04bb494413c39a20","tid":1909103,"uid":193361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:33:48.000Z","msg":"你估美國少野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:37:01.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲諗住旨意美帝？"},{"pid":"6a5037d2da31d1ca269255a0e5da49007c74f1c6","tid":1909103,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e1b3ff93733e365683a504f9e30f77b472b010","tid":1909103,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:43:43.000Z","msg":"湖北果埋有隔離<br />\n每日一千幾百從鬼國入境果班先驚，周圍走"},{"pid":"5341da5f7741346cb41fceaa2b928aac4f83fc9c","tid":1909103,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep